coverage, with both short-range street level views, and mid- to long-range =
environmental views
* Eight ultrasonic sensors for front and rear obstacle avoidance

Of course, there are a few others that we=E2=80=99re not counting (encoders=
 or hall sensors at the wheels; steering angle sensors; throttle and brake =
